reviewText:
Fantastic game.
Gorgeous art style;
Great atmosphere;
Marvelous sound design;
Easy to learn, really f'cking hard, near impossible to master;

It's like an arcade shooter, horde mode style, made by Satan.

One good run and you can get +1200 positions on the leaderboards.
Congratulations for being on the 3 thousand and something right now!
Now cry to yourself at night for not being able to do that again...
Congrats now you are back on the 5 thousand and something again because the game is good and more people are playing it and being better than you.
